{"tid":1885531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鍾南山料全國病例本月中下旬達峰值 但不代表病例之後會馬上下降","createTime":"2020-02-18T11:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T11:29:44.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fca4f6f5fc488287a4cab6d46b4c36194c9ff001","tid":1885531,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:03:59.000Z","msg":"國家衛健委公佈，全國確診新型冠狀病毒肺炎人數累計超過7萬2千宗，超過1800人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n國家衛健委高級別專家組組長鍾南山預計，全國病例在本月中下旬達到峰值，但不代表病例之後會馬上下降。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，目前武漢仍是關鍵，看來病毒還未停止人傳人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509303-20200218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509303-20200218.htm&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=1dd8dbc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509303-20200218.htm&h=d4d649a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509303-20200218.htm</a>"},{"pid":"71c3665e97a611387006d61f70269c9d9f4afa89","tid":1885531,"uid":84481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:06:39.000Z","msg":"彈出又彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3b97b6c07bf4925c5ab1fc3ffd81b128cfbb5d","tid":1885531,"uid":25260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"未來14天十分關鍵"},{"pid":"a40daaa6404cb55efcdefadc20015d4607adfecd","tid":1885531,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />14日左幾多次"},{"pid":"d69b2459ac308046243b0c1dee4671c8850297fd","tid":1885531,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"9up無極限"}]}